    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels like everything is so heavy. like, if I could just fade out or stop fighting for a second, it wouldn't even be a tragedy. it would just be quiet. i feel like i'm just waiting for the end anyway, and honestly, the idea of just not being here anymore sounds way more peaceful than this.",
